'''John H. Abeles, MD''' is an American-based [[venture investor]], director, consultant, entrepreneur, and philanthropist.

He is a Director of the International Opera Alliance, New York<ref>{{cite web|url=http://operaalliance.org/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=4&Itemid=14|title=Leadership|publisher=International Opera Alliance|accessdate=29 July 2010}}</ref> and a member of the Players Club, New York, which is given to the promulgation of the dramatic and performance arts. He also on the  board of the New Group, a theater organization in New York.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thenewgroup.org/board.htm|title=Board of Directors|publisher=The New Group|accessdate=29 July 2010}}</ref> 
